sources.title: Dicktator. The 1974 Paul Daniels Yolanda Beckham Linda York Ann Perry Vickie Cri
sources.description: Penned by Walt Davis and released in 1974 or 1977. Parody of various political figures of the time including Rose Mary Woods and the infamous missing tape.   Plot revolves around a male birth control that is too successful. A search for men who did not take the pill ensues.
